Since we know $DE$ and $DC$, we can now find the area of triangle $CDE$.  The desired area is $\frac{27/4 \cdot 9}{2}=\frac{243}{8}=30.375$.  This value, rounded to the nearest integer as requested, is $\boxed{30}$.

